22 January 2021 The management of departments and entities led by the late Minister in the Presidency, Jackson Mthembu will pay their respects through a drive-by visit to his family residence in Ackerville, Witbank today, Friday 22 January 2021 at 15h00. The management will address the family from across the street. The drive-by and address will occur in line with strict Covid-19 protocols. The following departments and entities reported to the late Minister: He steered the ship with transparency, commitment and confidence. He always served the people of South Africa unreservedly. May his soul rest in peace.  Hamba  Kahle Minister Mthembu Enquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139